reports/agent_reports/stage_03_shared_engine/attempt_01/ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW.md:108:- `arch_timing_probe.log`: `2024-01-01` bar has `bar_end` and documented `open(t+1)` at `2024-01-02T00:00:00+00:00`, but current clock and fill timestamp are `2024-01-03T00:00:00+00:00`.
